  intro:{nl:'Tailoring heeft <strong>4 bomen</strong>. <em>Nimble Needlework</em> is verplicht voor alle serieuze Tailors — dagelijkse bolt cooldowns en cloth drops. <em>Sin\'dorei Finery</em> voor Epic cloth armor. <em>Fabric Specialist</em> voor cloth drops + verborgen Multicraft-node. <em>Fiber Arts</em> voor skill-bonus op alle crafts.',en:"Tailoring has <strong>4 trees</strong>. <em>Nimble Needlework</em> is mandatory for all serious Tailors — daily bolt cooldowns and cloth drops. <em>Sin'dorei Finery</em> for Epic cloth armor. <em>Fabric Specialist</em> for cloth drops + hidden Multicraft node. <em>Fiber Arts</em> for skill bonus on all crafts.",da:"Tailoring har <strong>4 træer</strong>. Nimble Needlework er obligatorisk. Sin'dorei Finery til Epic klæderustning. Fabric Specialist til klæddrop. Fiber Arts til færdighedsbonus."},
